description: Naspers Limited operates in the consumer internet industry worldwide. It operates through Classifieds, Food Delivery, Payments and Fintech, Etail, Edtech, and Other Ecommerce segments. It holds investments in classifieds, food delivery, payments and fintech, education, health, and ecommerce, as well as ventures, and social and internet platforms; and offers eMAG platform for online food and grocery delivery network. The company also prints, publishes, and distributes newspapers, magazines, and books through digital platforms, as well as provides media logistics. Naspers Limited was founded in 1915 and is headquartered in Cape Town, South Africa.
